metadata.name: Cyber bat of cyber Street #1/10
metadata.description:
Little Bat spends time at the technology company where his father works, and one day, he sneaks into a secret laboratory and gets connected to a brain-linked computer system for an unknown reason.The system reads the data in Little Bat's brain and gives him cyber powers. He can now control computer systems, move in the cyber world, and hack into human brains.Bat learns to control these powers and starts fighting as Cyber-Bat. However, over time, the control of his cyber powers becomes difficult, and Bat drifts towards the dark side.As Cyber-Bat fights against evil people, he also has to struggle with himself. Eventually, he manages to regain control and continues to use his powers to eliminate evil.

"Art work by Erdogan Paksoy"
